{"pin":"BH00223","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00223","anchor":"","title":"Lawh-i-Hikmat (Tablet of Wisdom)","first_line":"This is an Epistle which the All-Merciful hath sent down from the Kingdom of Utterance. It is truly a breath of life… Say: Magnified be Thy Name, O Lord my God!","first_line_orig":"کتاب انزله الرحمن من ملکوت البیان و انه لروح الحیوان لاهل الامکان تعالی الله  ","language":"1","word_count":"2680","subjects":"@Greek philosophers; Greek civilization, @Word of God sanctified from time and place, @special knowledge of the Manifestation of God, @consorting with all; being kind; loving to all, @heat and motion, @the divine emanation; the all-pervading bounty of God, @corruption and decline of Islam; of the Shi'ih, @purpose; goal of creation, @walking the spiritual path; spiritual wayfaring; the virtuous life","notes":" \u003ca href=\"https://d9263461.github.io/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V4/Contents.html\"\u003eROB4.033 et al\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://bluefin.live/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/BKOG.pdf#page=23\"\u003eBKOG.382\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://www.bahai.org/r/777210373\"\u003eGPB.219\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://adibmasumian.files.wordpress.com/2023/04/ebtb.pdf#page=115\"\u003eEBTB.115\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://bahai-library.com/bahailib/1504.pdf#page=97\"\u003eMMAH.085\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://reference.bahai.org/fa/t/o/GS/gs-139.html\"\u003eGSH.139\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#116\"\u003eLL#116\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"}]},{"code":"BH00223BLE","anchor":"ble","translations":[{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban